<br>
&quot;You men never cease to amaze me.&quot;<br>
<br>
&lt;trotting up to the necromancer, Salvia sits on her white haunches and wags her tail.  The snow white fur that covers its lengths fade into a deep black at the tips.  Eyeing the newcomer, she raises a paw&gt;<br>
<br>
&quot;Hail, I am Salvia, also an elder here.  Welcome to the hall, I also know a thing or two about sibling rivalry to its darkest depths, as you have said here today.  We have some common ground, you and I.  Glad to have you here, and if those Barbarians get too out of hand let me know&quot;<br>
